attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: "{'query': \"SELECT \\n    SUM(SL_AM) as total_amount,\\n    strftime('%Y-%m', substr(SL_DT, 1, 4) || '-' || substr(SL_DT, 5, 2) || '-' || substr(SL_DT, 7, 2)) as month,\\n    SUM(SL_AM) as monthly_amount\\nFROM WBM_T_BLL_SPEC_IZ \\nWHERE ACCTNO = '70018819695' \\nAND BLL_MC_NM LIKE '%스타벅스%'\\nAND SL_DT BETWEEN '20240701' AND '20240930'\\nGROUP BY month\\nORDER BY month;\"}"
